workouts.name: Stretching
workouts.description: Stretch your arms, legs, and back to improve flexibility and prevent injury.

workouts.name: Plank
workouts.description: Get into a push-up position with your hands directly under your shoulders. Hold your body in a straight line from head to heels.

workouts.name: Jumping Jacks
workouts.description: Stand with your feet together and your hands at your sides. Jump up and spread your legs while raising your arms above your head. Jump back to the starting position.

workouts.name: Push-ups
workouts.description: Get into a plank position with your hands shoulder-width apart. Lower your body until your chest touches the ground, then push back up.

workouts.name: Squats
workouts.description: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your arms at your sides. Lower your body by bending your knees and pushing your hips back, then return to the starting position.
